@startuml system-context
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
  BorderColor #0277BD
}

title System Context - SRS Review Agent
actor "🟦 Regulatory Lead" as Reg
actor "🟨 Risk Eng" as Risk
actor "🟨 UX Owner" as UX
actor "🟨 Cyber Eng" as Cyber
actor "🟨 AI Eng" as AI
actor "🟢 SRS Owner" as SRSOwner
actor "QA/Reg" as QA

rectangle "SRS Review Agent" {
  component "Core Engine" as Engine
}

cloud "Document Repository /\nVersion Control" as DocRepo
database "Document Management\nSystem (DMS)" as DMS
rectangle "Workflow / Notification\nSystem" as Notify

Reg --> Engine : baseline docs
Risk --> Engine : baseline docs
UX --> Engine : baseline docs
Cyber --> Engine : baseline docs
AI --> Engine : baseline docs

DocRepo --> Engine : new SRS changes
Engine --> DMS : check references
Engine --> Notify : findings → owners
Notify --> Reg
Notify --> Risk
Notify --> UX
Notify --> Cyber
Notify --> AI
Notify --> SRSOwner

note right of Engine
  Monitors SRS → notifies
  document owners based
  on change impact matrix
end note

@enduml
